\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11676149 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 Oh very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5992378 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 Was she very motherly, affectionate?
