\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5992378 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 Is that the only time that she really went at you?
