\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240  teas and - I always liked to be where there was a tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5992378 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 So you took part in most of these teas and things that the chapel organised?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11676149 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 Yes - as a consumer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5992378 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 Did you belong to the choir at any time?
