ou'd to memorize a certain lot and when you'd memorized them - sufficiently for the adjudicator you got a Lord }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7229505\charrsid2455240 Wharton\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 
 Bible.
