\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5992378 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 Was that a sort of temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11676149 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 Well - yes, yes, it was a - it was a national affair, the Band of Hope you know. And there was like a branch
 at the - for ought I know, there was a branch at the Sunday school and - you signed the pledge.
