\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5992378 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 That says what their purpose is?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11676149 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5992378 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 But do you remember what you used to do in the Boys Brigade, how often you used to meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11676149 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 Once a week. Once a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5992378 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 What did you used to do at the meetings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11676149 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 Drill. Have a little talk. On the Bible. And of course, band practice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5992378 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 Did you used to play in the band?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11676149 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5992378 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 What did you play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11676149 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 The big drum. In fact I had a go at all the instruments. I ended up with the big drum.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5992378 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 Did they ever have any outings from the Boys Brigade?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11676149 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 Yes. Oh yes. Once summer I went to - to camp at - Auburn, near Bridlington. There was a camp there. A - Auburn.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5992378 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 That was just one year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11676149 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 Near Bridlington. One week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5992378 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 A full week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11676149 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5992378 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 Did they take you on day trips ever?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11676149 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 No, we used to have - we used to have - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7229505\charrsid2455240 battalion}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
