\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11676149 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 Yes, the Bradford }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7229505\charrsid2455240 Battalion}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 , you see, and our chapel was number three company.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5992378 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 And you used to visit other chapels?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11676149 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5992378 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 And march there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11676149 JC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12149258\charrsid2455240 Yes. And the great popular chapels were those that provided a bun and tea. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
